<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div
        style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #e1e4e8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #059669;">🏢 Onsite Meeting: {{meeting_title}}</h2>
        <p>Hi <strong>{{user_name}}</strong>, we'll see you at the office for this session.</p>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{meeting_date}} at {{meeting_time}}</p>
        </div>

        {{#if is_recurring}}
        <div style="background: #fffbeb; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <p style="margin:0; font-size: 14px;">🔄 <strong>Recurring:</strong> {{recurring_detail}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Our AI will be active to capture the minutes of the meeting live.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>